# Theme tokens (`src/styles.scss` + `src/styles/_interaction.scss`)

Portal and shared UI use a **4-layer surface stack** mirrored semantically in light and dark. Do not hardcode hex in component SCSS — use CSS variables from `styles.scss`. Do not reintroduce flat dark chrome or translucent card backgrounds.

## Surface layers

| Layer | Token | Light | Dark | Used by |
|-------|-------|-------|------|---------|
| Chrome | `--bg-chrome` | `#ffffff` | `#0b0f19` | sidebar, topbar |
| Canvas | `--bg-app` | `#f1f5f9` | `#0d1220` | body, portal scroll area, hub tab sticky bg |
| Surface | `--bg-surface` | `#ffffff` | `#151c2e` | cards, table shell, form sections, dialogs |
| Inset | `--bg-inset` | `#f8fafc` | `#111827` | filter toolbar band, table header row |
| Control | `--bg-control` | `#ffffff` | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | inputs, filter search/buttons, form fields |

**Aliases** (prefer semantic tokens in new code; aliases exist for backward compat):

- `--bg-sidebar`, `--bg-topbar` → `--bg-chrome`
- `--bg-form-card`, `--bg-table-card`, `--bg-confirm-dialog`, `--bg-detail-modal`, `--bg-table-filter-panel`, `--bg-sidebar-flyout` → `--bg-surface`
- `--bg-form-input`, `--bg-table-control` → `--bg-control`
- `--bg-table-filter-toolbar`, `--bg-table-header` → `--bg-inset`
- `--bg-table-filter-chips` → `--bg-surface`

**Card emphasis (both themes):** surfaces contrast with canvas. In light, surface equals chrome; in dark, surface is intentionally lighter than chrome/canvas.

**Elevation:** light surfaces may use `--shadow-surface` (`0 1px 3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06)`); dark uses border + color step only (`--shadow-surface: none`).

## Table filter toolbar stack

Inside `DataTableComponent` (`.data-table-card`):

```text
Surface (--bg-surface)
  └─ Inset toolbar band (--bg-inset) — search left, Filter/Clear right
       └─ Control inputs (--bg-control)
  └─ Chips row (--bg-surface)
  └─ Inset table header (--bg-inset)
  └─ Rows — hover via --bg-table-row-hover
```

Active filters: left `3px` accent on `.data-table-filters--active` — no count badge on toggle (see `table-filters.mdc`).

**User hub tables:** when `DataTableComponent` has `entityTab`, filter toolbar **always** shows entity `2px` top + `3px` left accent (`--entity-filter-accent`) — not only when filters active. See `entity-service-colors.mdc`.

Search input focus: `--border-form-input-focus` (not `--text-muted`).

## Typography scale

Defined in `:root` / theme blocks — use instead of hardcoded `font-size` / `font-weight` in shared UI:

| Token | Value | Typical use |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| `--font-size-page-title` | `1.5rem` (`--font-size-page-title-mobile`: `1.25rem`) | `PageTitleComponent` h1 |
| `--font-size-section-title` | `1.125rem` (`--font-size-section-title-mobile`: `1rem`) | form section h2, dialog title |
| `--font-size-card-title` | `1rem` | intent card, metric card title |
| `--font-size-body` | `0.875rem` | body, subtitles, buttons, tabs |
| `--font-size-body-sm` | `0.8125rem` | hints, back link, filter controls |
| `--font-size-caption` | `0.75rem` | status badges, filter active count |
| `--font-size-overline` | `0.6875rem` | sidebar section titles, journey group labels |
| `--font-weight-regular` … `--font-weight-bold` | 400–700 | semantic weights |
| `--line-height-tight` / `snug` / `normal` | 1.2 / 1.35 / 1.5 | |
| `--letter-spacing-tight` / `--letter-spacing-overline` | page titles / uppercase labels |

**Text roles:**

- `--text-primary` — headings, body
- `--text-muted` — subtitles, helpers
- `--text-section` — overline labels (uppercase nav section titles)
- `--text-secondary` — alias of `--text-muted`; default state for text links
- `--table-cell-primary-color` — always `var(--text-primary)` (no separate dark body color)

## Interaction tokens

In `styles.scss`:

- `--transition-fast: 0.15s ease`
- `--border-hover: var(--text-muted)`
- `--bg-hover-subtle: var(--bg-active)`
- `--bg-hover-row: var(--bg-table-row-hover)`
- `--bg-primary-hover` — `color-mix` on `--bg-form-btn-primary` per theme (not opacity)
- `--shadow-hover-surface: var(--shadow-table-actions-menu)`

Mixins in `src/styles/_interaction.scss` — `@use 'styles/interaction' as interaction;`:

| Mixin | Use for |
|-------|---------|
| `interactive-surface` | Clickable cards (intent `--clickable`, quick-action, metric link wrapper) — border + shadow hover; **no `translateY` lift** |
| `interactive-text-link` | Text links — `--text-secondary` → `--text-primary` + underline on hover/focus |
| `interactive-control` | Tabs, filter buttons, outlined controls — `--bg-hover-subtle` fill |
| `interactive-primary-btn` | Primary CTAs — `--bg-primary-hover` (not `opacity: 0.92`) |
| `focus-ring-neutral` | Portal focus rings — `outline: 2px solid var(--text-muted)`; **not `--portal-accent`** on portal content |

**Hover rules (do not regress):**

1. No `translateY` / card lift on portal dashboard or content cards.
2. No opacity-only primary button hover — use `--bg-primary-hover`.
3. Secondary buttons: `--bg-hover-row` or `--bg-hover-subtle`.
4. Text links: color shift + underline (never opacity alone).
5. Table rows / mobile cards: `--bg-table-row-hover`.
6. Portal page content: neutral focus rings and hovers — `--portal-accent` is **sidebar only** (see `layout.mdc`).

