## Do not

- Hardcode hex colors in component SCSS when a token exists.
- Use `--bg-card` (undefined) — use `--bg-surface`.
- Set dark `--bg-table-card: transparent` or translucent `--bg-form-card` overlays for main content panels.
- Add `translateY(-1px)` hover lift on portal cards.
- Use `opacity: 0.92` for primary button hover in portal.
- Use `--portal-accent` for focus rings or hovers on portal page content (cards, links, buttons).
- Duplicate typography sizes in new shared widgets — use the scale tokens.
- Import interaction mixins into very large SCSS files if it pushes past component budget — inline equivalent token-based rules instead (see `data-table.component.scss`).

